使用方程 $\ln{[\text{N}_2\text{O}_5]_t} = -kt + \ln{[\text{N}_2\text{O}_5]_0}$:

\begin{align*}
\ln{[\text{N}_2\text{O}_5]_{1500}} &= -5.40 \times 10^{-4} \, \mathrm{s}^{-1} \times (1500 \, \mathrm{s}) + \ln{(0.250)} \\
&= -2.20 \\
[\text{N}_2\text{O}_5]_{1500} &= 0.111 \, \mathrm{M}
\end{align*}

